						<summary>

						<p>Kūrattaḷvār shrine, west wall, proper left.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1474, Parīdhāvi, Śrāvaṇa ba. Śrījayaṁti</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1552 A.D. August 12, Friday, 78, f.d.n. 21.</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to refer to an endowment of money made by Kuruchēṭi Śrīraṅgarāja to the shrine of Kūrattāḻvār.</p>						

						</summary>
